Klasse Rocket:

    Instanziierung der Rocket-Klasse
    Festlegen der Raketen-Attribute (z. B. Größe, Farbe, Muster)
    Starten der Rakete (Triggerung durch Mausklick/Touch)
    a. Aufruf der Explosion-Methode
    b. Übergeben der Raketenattribute an die Explosion-Klasse

Klasse Explosion:

    Instanziierung der Explosion-Klasse
    Verarbeiten der übergebenen Raketenattribute
    Initialisierung der Partikel
    a. Instanziierung der Partikel-Klasse für jedes Partikel
    b. Übergeben der Explosionattribute an die Partikel-Klasse

Klasse Particle:

    Instanziierung der Partikel-Klasse
    Verarbeiten der übergebenen Explosionattribute
    Berechnung der Bewegungsmuster der Partikel
    Anzeige der Partikel auf dem Bildschirm






For the class Rocket, an activity diagram could show the following steps:

    The user selects the properties of the rocket, such as size, color, and pattern.
    The rocket is instantiated with the user-defined properties.
    The user triggers the launch of the rocket by clicking or tapping on the screen.
    The rocket's launch method is called, which calculates the trajectory and triggers the explosion.

For the class Explosion, the activity diagram could show the following steps:

    The explosion is instantiated with the properties defined in the rocket, such as the size of the explosion radius, the number of particles, and the movement pattern.
    The explosion method is called, which creates the individual particles and animates them according to their properties.
    The particles are displayed on the screen and slowly fade away.

For the class Particle, the activity diagram could show the following steps:

    The particle is instantiated with properties such as color, size, and life span.
    The particle's movement is calculated based on its properties and the explosion's properties.
    The particle is displayed on the screen and slowly fades away as its life span decreases.